UPDATE: The police have thanked the public for their help. The man is on his way to have an interview with the police. ————————————————————————————- MBOMBELA – It is believed that the man pictured can assist police in a culpable homicide investigation. This after a hit-and-run claimed the life of a local woman on Saturday night at around 23:00 in Loco Street.  READ MORE: Witnesses sought after hit-and-run in Mbombela Anyone who can assist police in this matter is requested to contact Bossies Community Justice on 082-567-5212 or Lt Col Erhard Ströh 082-464-5721 or Const Paul Ngxam on 079-764-9840.